SYNOPSIS
      xman <topic>

DESCRIPTION
      Searches in some special directories under /doc for the given topic
      or command. If there are two equal topics in different directories
      the one found first will be printed.

EXAMPLES
      xman xman
      xman xforall
      xman efun/destruct
      xman w/destruct
      xman move
      xman thing
      xman domains

